你能够调用以下的API:
[['FinancePolicySearch.find_policies', {'name': 'FinancePolicySearch.find_policies', 'description': 'This function searches for financial support policies based on category and focus.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'category', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The category of the policy, e.g., environmental_tech.'}, {'name': 'focus', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The focus of the policy, e.g., innovation.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'policies', 'description': 'A list of up to three matching policies, each with an ID, category, and focus.'}]}], ['FinancePolicySearch.get_policy_details', {'name': 'FinancePolicySearch.get_policy_details', 'description': 'This function retrieves detailed information about a specific financial policy given its ID.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'policyId', 'type': 'NUMBER', 'description': 'The ID of the financial policy.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'details', 'description': 'Detailed information about the policy, including measures and scope.'}]}], ['FinanceDataAccess.fetch_financing_data', {'name': 'FinanceDataAccess.fetch_financing_data', 'description': 'This function fetches financing data for a specific industry.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'industry', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The industry for which financing data is requested.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'data', 'description': 'Financing data for the requested industry.'}]}], ['DataAnalysis.assess_impact', {'name': 'DataAnalysis.assess_impact', 'description': 'This function assesses the impact of a financial policy on a specific industry.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'policyId', 'type': 'NUMBER', 'description': 'The ID of the financial policy.'}, {'name': 'industryData', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The industry data to assess the impact against.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'impact', 'description': 'The assessed impact of the policy on the industry.'}]}]]
请生成一个解决用户问题的计划，计划应该是一个行为列表，每个行为的格式如下:

[{
    // 动作的ID
    "id": number;
    // 动作要调用的API名称
    "name": string;
    // 当前API的参数输入(JSON格式)
    "args": "str(Record<string, any>)";
}, ...
]

你可以在计划中想象参数的值，这些指令将按顺序执行。
例如，如果你想调用 `FinancePolicySearch.find_policies` 并传入 `category` 和 `focus`，你可以写下面的计划:

[{
    "id": 0,
    "name": "FinancePolicySearch.find_policies",
    "args": "{'category': 'environmental_tech', 'focus': 'innovation'}",
}, ...
]

这些参数将在执行时被替换为真实的值。请注意，参数应该是一个字符串，而不是一个字典。
请在字典的参数中使用 ''，在其他地方使用 ""，不要打印值为 None 或 null 的参数。

你应该只生成一个 JSON 格式的计划列表。列表应该是完整的计划列表，不要有 `...`。
不要生成任何解释 JSON 的文本。
